Tests for Form::Data::Processor::Field::clear_empty
Tests for Form::Data::Processor::Field::Repeatable

Form::Data::Processor::Role::Fields/init_input remove 'confess'

Add fields:
    1. Text
        Make `trim` optional

        1.1 String
            Like Text, but oneliner

            1.1.1 Number
                Number with `min`, `max`, 'positive', 'negative', 'allow_zero' attributes
                Should inflate ("numify") input from string to number.

                1.1.1.1 Integer
                    Must be a number without decimal part

                1.1.1.2 Float
                    Must be a number with decimal part
                    Also add `precision` attribute

            1.1.2 Email

            1.1.3 DateTime
                Datetime in ISO-8601 format
                With `min`, `max` attributes

                1.1.3.1 Date

                1.1.3.2 Time

    2. Boolean
        Add true and false values.
        Example:
            'YES' is true
            'NO'  is false
            Otherwise, field doesn't have value
